            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "There are expensive, internal things done unnecessarily on each cursor moved, not only matchparen. There is still lots of room for improvement here.\r\n\r\nThe general idea of skipping highlight updates entirely until cursor is idle for xxx milliseconds, is very high-leverage and we absolutely should do that.",
